'''Annette''' is the girlfriend of [[Cynthia]].

==History==
Annette came to the hospital when her girlfriend, Cynthia, has a transient ischemic attack. It was during this visit that Cynthia told her son, [[Seth]], that they were together. Seth left in anger and seeing how upset Cynthia was, Annette told Same to get him back, saying that Cynthia would move to Florida with Seth since she needed her son and grandchildren more than she needed Annette. However, Seth returned and said that he realized that she'd spent her life taking care of him and his father and now she needed to do something for herself. He said she could stay and they'd visit each other.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She and [[Cynthia]] have been seeing each other secretly since they met when their kids were young.

===Familial===
She has a child who is the same age as [[Seth]].
